title: Aiseesoft Total Video Converter Platinum 7.1.26 [ChingLiu]
description:
Powerful video converter software

Convert any video to all popular video formats - Aiseesoft Total Video Converter can easily convert all video formats including MP4, H.264/MP4 AVC, MTS, MXF, MOV, AVI, DivX, XviD, WMV, MKV, FLV, WTV, VOB and HD video such as HD WMV, HD MKV, HD DivX, HD XviD, HD MOV, HD FLV, HD MP4, etc.

Convert any video to 3D video formats - This video conversion software can convert any video to 3D formats easily. It offers up to 14 types of 3D modes including Anaglyph 3D (10 types), Side By Side (Half-Width/Full) 3D, Top and Bottom (Half-Height/Full) 3D.

Support all popular media player software - Most Media Player software like Window Media Player only supports video formats like AVI, MP4, WMV, etc. To play any video file on your media players, just convert it to video/audio formats compatible with your media player.

Support almost all popular portable devices - It can convert all video files to iPod, iPhone, iPad, Apple TV, Samsung Galaxy S4, Samsung Galaxy Note 2, HTC One, PSP, PS3, Xbox360, Sony Xperia, etc.

Professional audio converter - This comprehensive and powerful piece of video conversion software can convert any audio format or extract audio track from video to AAC, AC3, AIFF, AMR, AU, FLAC, MP3, M4V, MP2, OGG, WAV, WMA audio formats.

Convert video and audio files in batches - You are able to convert several files to different formats with only one conversion.

Edit video effect

Video effect modifier - You can get your desired video quality by modifying video Brightness, Contrast, Saturation, Hue and Volume. Also this total video converter owns the technique to eliminate some jaggedness from the interlaced video for better viewing.

Video cutter - Aiseesoft Total Video Converter possesses "Trim" function to help you cut a clip from the original video. You can set the "Start Time" and "End Time" to define the segment.

Video cropper - The Video conversion software allows you to adjust video playing area. You can also select the aspect ratio to extrude your video slightly.

Video Merger - It enables you to merge multiple videos into one video.

Watermark - With this professional video converter, adding a text or image watermark to your video will be a very easy thing. You can adjust its size, font, color, position and transparency.

Audio track, subtitle, output settings

Create different movies and music quality - You can define video settings, such as Video Encoder, Frame Rate, Video Bitrate, Resolution, and audio settings, including Audio Encoder, Sample Rate, Channels, Audio Bitrate. As for the Resolution, if you don't find what you want, you are available to input your own resolution in Width(pixels) * Height(pixels). All the settings can be saved in the option list of "User-Defined".

Select audio track and subtitle - It supplies you with audio track and subtitle choice. You can choose any audio track and subtitle for the output video.

Quick, easy way to convert video files

Preview and Snapshot - With Aiseesoft Total Video Converter, you can preview the original video and output video effect. Once you get one desired movie scene, you can take a snapshot and save it as a picture.
